      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for those. that helps a lot. my students are still worried though, they're asking how to respond to the counter-argument that these policies just cause human rights violations or make the process more inhumane. can you give me a quick summary of why those criticisms are usually considered valid or what the main flaws are in the pro-enforcement stance from a humanitarian perspective?",
